#

Creamy Pumpkin Risotto

40 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodEasyQuick

Description

A rich and creamy risotto infused with the delightful flavors of pumpkin, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • pumpkin puree: 1 cup
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • onion, diced: 1 small
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • parmesan cheese, grated: 1/2 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • nutmeg: a pinch
